  - m_Id: 1000000000054
    m_Localized: "E"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000055
    m_Localized: "...Did I make it out?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000056
    m_Localized: "Is this place... over?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000057
    m_Localized: "Why is my heart still afraid...?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000058
    m_Localized: "...Then why can I still hear their voices?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000059
    m_Localized: "Come back..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000060
    m_Localized: "Xayrulla... did you make it out...?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000065
    m_Localized: "— Latest News — Early this morning, a 27-year-old man named Xayrulla was found dead inside the elevator of an old apartment building in the city. According to neighbors, he had not left his apartment for nearly a week. However, during the investigation, almost no evidence was found that he had actually been living there during that time. Specialists are still trying to answer one question: was Xayrulla really inside his apartment for an entire week, or had he been wandering inside an unknown place people now call the “Luminal Trap”? The most disturbing part is that this is not the first incident. Over the past few months, the number of mysterious elevator-related cases has increased rapidly. Witnesses claim that before the incidents, the victims began talking to themselves and said they were receiving letters from unknown people. The police still cannot provide an official explanation for these events. However, one name is spreading more and more across the internet — “Luminal Trap.” Some believe it is a psychological disorder, while others claim that people who enter that place slowly begin to lose their sense of reality. And the strangest part of all — every recovered letter ended with the names of the victims themselves."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000021
    m_Localized: "I couldn't sleep again today..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000022
    m_Localized: "Maybe it's because I haven't left the apartment for a week."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000023
    m_Localized: "A little walk might clear my head."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000024
    m_Localized: "Something feels wrong..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000025
    m_Localized: "My head feels weird."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000026
    m_Localized: "$2d#... what is this, a floor number?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000027
    m_Localized: "I haven't left home for a week and now the elevator's losing its mind too?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000028
    m_Localized: "Whatever... fine."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000029
    m_Localized: "What's happening?!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000030
    m_Localized: "Stop... STOP!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000031
    m_Localized: "I SAID STOP!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000032
    m_Localized: "What the hell is happening?!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000033
    m_Localized: "FOOD"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000034
    m_Localized: "TURN BACK"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000035
    m_Localized: "LIES"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000036
    m_Localized: "REGRET"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000037
    m_Localized: "THEY HAVE ALWAYS BEEN WATCHING YOU"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000038
    m_Localized: "DON'T GO DOWN"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000039
    m_Localized: "HIDE YOUR FEAR"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000040
    m_Localized: "...Where am I?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000041
    m_Localized: "What happened to me..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000042
    m_Localized: "This is all because of those damn tomatoes."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000043
    m_Localized: "I knew they were spoiled... I shouldn't have eaten them."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000044
    m_Localized: "Wait... what the hell?!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000045
    m_Localized: "They messed up the elevator too."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000046
    m_Localized: "Why are you showing floor 0 now?!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1000000000047
    m_Localized: "I need to get out of here fast."
